thread.title_full: BRIEF-Sophie Baratte appointed Cellnovo CEO | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Sophie Baratte appointed Cellnovo CEO
text:
Oct 9 Cellnovo Group SA :
* Cellnovo expands its organisation
* Sophie Baratte appointed CEO
* Cellnovo executive chairman to transition to non-executive chairman
* Didier Lenormand joins Cellnovo as interim CFO in replacement of Bart Bergstein who has left company Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
